    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Wallball]]></title>
    <link href="http://joanperals.com/2013/wallball/"/>
    <updated>2013-07-20T23:19:04+02:00</updated>
    <id>http://joanperals.com/2013/wallball</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Wallball is a simple gesture-based game made with Box2D and Processing.</p>

<!--more-->


<p>Draw lines which will become &ldquo;walls&rdquo;. These &ldquo;walls&rdquo; need to touch one ball of each colour (red, green and blue) in order to disappear. When a wall disappears it will give you points.</p>

<p>But be careful to not get the balls trapped between your walls and the top of the screen! When this happens the game will end.</p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/jperals/wallball">Read more</a> or <a href="http://jperals.github.io/wallball/">just play</a>.</p>
]]></content>
